14 (a) (1) The Department shall ensure that at any given time at least 50% of the
15 eligible individuals receiving financial assistance under the Program are:
16 (i) gainfully employed;
17 (ii) actively seeking employment; or
18 (iii) attending an institution of postsecondary or higher education, as
