25 (ii) are certified by an attending physician, PHYSICIAN ASSISTANT,
26 or certified nurse practitioner as being at risk of placement in a nursing facility or similar
27 institution licensed to provide chronic or intermediate care if attendant care services are
28 not received in the community.

